    "The insulin suspension period has ended.\n\nYou can resume delivery from the banner on the home screen or from your pump settings screen. You will be reminded again in 15 minutes." : {
      "comment" : "Alert content body for suspendEnded pod alert",
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "ar" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "The insulin suspension period has ended.\n\nYou can resume delivery from the banner on the home screen or from your pump settings screen. You will be reminded again in 15 minutes."
          }
        },
        "cs" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Období pozastavení podávání inzulínu skončilo.\n\nPodávání můžete obnovit z banneru na domovské obrazovce nebo z obrazovky nastavení pumpy. Za 15 minut vám bude znovu připomenuta."
          }
        },
        "da" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Perioden for suspension af insulin er afsluttet.\n\nDu kan genoptage afgivelsen fra den øverste del af startskærmen eller fra skærmen med pumpeindstillinger. Du vil blive mindet om dette igen om 15 minutter."
          }
        },
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Die Insulinabschaltung ist beendet.\n\nSie können die Abgabe über das Banner auf dem Startbildschirm oder über den Bildschirm mit den Pumpeneinstellungen fortsetzen. Sie werden in 15 Minuten erneut erinnert."
          }
        },
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "The insulin suspension period has ended.\n\nYou can resume delivery from the banner on the home screen or from your pump settings screen. You will be reminded again in 15 minutes."
          }
        },
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "El periodo de suspensión de la insulina ha finalizado.\n\nPuedes reanudar la administración desde el banner de la pantalla de inicio o desde la pantalla de ajustes de tu bomba. Se le recordará de nuevo en 15 minutos."
          }
        },
        "fi" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "The insulin suspension period has ended.\n\nYou can resume delivery from the banner on the home screen or from your pump settings screen. You will be reminded again in 15 minutes."
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "La période de suspension de l'insuline est terminée. \n\nVous pouvez relancer l'administration à partir de la bannière sur l'écran d'accueil ou à partir de l'écran des paramètres de votre pompe. Vous recevrez un nouveau rappel dans 15 minutes."
          }
        },
        "he" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "The insulin suspension period has ended.\n\nYou can resume delivery from the banner on the home screen or from your pump settings screen. You will be reminded again in 15 minutes."
          }
        },
        "hu" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "The insulin suspension period has ended.\n\nYou can resume delivery from the banner on the home screen or from your pump settings screen. You will be reminded again in 15 minutes."
          }
        },
        "it" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Il periodo di sospensione dell'insulina è terminato. \n \nPuoi riprendere l'erogazione dal banner nella schermata iniziale o dalla schermata delle impostazioni della pompa. Riceverai un altro promemoria tra 15 minuti."
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "インスリンの中断期間は終了した。\n\nホーム画面のバナー、またはポンプ設定画面から投与を再開できます。15分後に再度リマインダーが表示されます。"
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "인슐린 일시 중단 기간이 종료되었습니다.\n\n홈 화면의 배너 또는 펌프 설정 화면에서 배송을 재개할 수 있습니다. 15분 후에 다시 알림이 표시됩니다."
          }
        },
        "nb" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Perioden med insulinsuspensjon er avsluttet.\n\nDu kan gjenoppta leveringen fra banneret på startskjermen eller fra skjermbildet for pumpeinnstillinger. Du vil bli påminnet igjen om 15 minutter."
          }
        },
        "nl" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "De insulineonderbrekingsperiode is verstreken.\n\nJe kunt de toediening hervatten op het startscherm of via je pompinstellingenscherm. Over 15 minuten wordt je er opnieuw aan herinnerd."
          }
        },
        "pl" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Okres zawieszenia podawania insuliny dobiegł końca. \n\nPodawanie można wznowić za pomocą banera na ekranie głównym lub na ekranie ustawień pompy. Ponowne przypomnienie pojawi się za 15 minut."
          }
        },
        "pt-BR" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "The insulin suspension period has ended.\n\nYou can resume delivery from the banner on the home screen or from your pump settings screen. You will be reminded again in 15 minutes."
          }
        },
        "ro" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Perioada de suspendarea a administrării de insulină s-a încheiat.\n\nPuteți relua administrarea din panoul de pe ecranul principal sau de pe ecranul de setări al pompei. Vi se va aminti din nou în 15 minute."
          }
        },
        "ru" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Период приостановки подачи инсулина закончилось.\n\nВы можете возобновить введение инсулина с баннера на главном экране приложения или с экрана настроек вашей помпы. Через 15 минут вы получите повторное напоминание."
          }
        },
        "sk" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Obdobie pozastavenia inzulínu sa skončilo.\n\nPodávanie inzulínu môžete obnoviť z bannera na domovskej obrazovke alebo z obrazovky nastavení pumpy. Pripomienka sa vám znova zobrazí o 15 minút."
          }
        },
        "sl" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Obdobje začasne ukinitve inzulina se je končalo.\n\nDostavljanje lahko obnovite s transparenta na začetnem zaslonu ali z zaslona z nastavitvami črpalke. Ponovno boste opomnjeni čez 15 minut."
          }
        },
        "sv" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Planerad period av paus av pump är slut.\n\nDu kan återuppta insulintillförsel i pumpinställningar. Du kommer bli påmind igen om 15 minuter."
          }
        },
        "tr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "İnsülin askıya alma süresi sona ermiştir.\n\nAna ekran üzerinden veya pompa ayarları ekranınızdan iletime devam edebilirsiniz. 15 dakika içinde tekrar hatırlatılacaktır."
          }
        },
        "uk" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "The insulin suspension period has ended.\n\nYou can resume delivery from the banner on the home screen or from your pump settings screen. You will be reminded again in 15 minutes."
          }
        },
        "vi" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Thời gian tạm dừng tiêm insulin đã kết thúc.\n\nBạn có thể tiếp tục tiêm từ thanh thông báo trên màn hình chính hoặc từ cài đặt bơm. Bạn sẽ nhận nhắc nhở lần nữa sau 15 phút."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "The insulin suspension period has ended.\n\nYou can resume delivery from the banner on the home screen or from your pump settings screen. You will be reminded again in 15 minutes."
          }
        }
      }
